      <t>&lt;p&gt;This memo presents the specification for version 7 of the Internet Protocol, as well as version 7 of the TCP and the user datagram protocol.  This memo defines an Experimental Protocol for the Internet community.  It does not specify an Internet standard.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
